children.value:
css({
	focusCircle: {
		position: 'absolute',
		width: 48,
		height: 48,
		backgroundColor: 'elevation',
		borderRadius: 24,
		opacity: 0,
		scaleX: 0,
		scaleY: 0,
		left: 0,
		display: 'inline-block',
		translateX: -14,
		translateY: -14,
	},
	focusCirclePrimary: { backgroundColor: 'primary' },
	focusCircle$invalid$touched: { backgroundColor: 'error' },
	focusCircle$hover: {
		scaleX: 1,
		scaleY: 1,
		translateX: -14,
		translateY: -14,
		opacity: 0.14,
	},
	focusCircle$focus: {
		scaleX: 1,
		scaleY: 1,
		translateX: -14,
		translateY: -14,
		opacity: 0.25,
	},
	focusCircle$disabled: { scaleX: 0, scaleY: 0 },
})
